      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple deep scratches, dents, and visible rust or corrosion in several areas. The interior is heavily worn, with damaged seating surfaces and a deteriorated headliner. Mechanical reliability is questionable and the vehicle will likely require significant repairs.",
      "price": 4500.0,
